description:
The Losers run out of gas outside Castle Rock as they discuss Stephen King’s Cujo.


Chapters include: Intro, The Hook/Structure and Format (8:00), Zeroes and Villains (1:03:50), The Sematary (2:10:00), Word Processor of the God (2:26:30), Poundcake! (2:36:00), King’s Dominion (2:51:00), Overall Thoughts(2:54:00), Adaptation (3:03:00), Outro (3:30:35).


Hosted on Acast. See acast.com/privacy for more information.
